[I] A nonogram logic game for KDE

[T] The goal is to reveal the hidden pattern in the board by coloring or
[T] leaving blank the cells in a grid according to numbers given at the side of
[T] the grid. This is a single player game.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/picmi/

[A] The KDE-Team
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

